{
  "texts": [
    "The experiment consisted of three trials for each participant, and each trial consisted of three steps.",
    "Table 1 shows a summary of the three steps in each trial.",
    "In Step 0, the computer presented the participants with a criminal case to be judged and the testimonies associated to it.",
    "In order to use standardized materials, we used the criminal cases of the ForenPsy 1.0 normative bank of testimonies developed by Álvarez et al. (2023).",
    "This bank includes the description of three criminal cases (homicide, threats, and trespassing) with 15 testimonies each."
  ]
}